This Privacy Policy describes Our policies and procedures on the collection, use and disclosure of Your information when You use any service related to Jupiter and tells You about Your privacy rights and how the law protects You. We use Your Personal data to improve our service and your experience. By using Jupiter, You agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
